{"id":147116,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/简讯：叙利亚枪杀参加葬礼民众/","date":"2011-04-24T07:00:21Z","modified":"2011-04-24T07:00:21Z","title":"简讯：叙利亚枪杀参加葬礼民众","content":"<div>\n<p>来自叙利亚的报道说，安全部队枪杀了至少9名参加反政府示威者葬礼的民众。</p>\n<p>据报道，叙利亚安全部队在该国首都大马士革、西部城市霍姆斯和南部城市伊斯拉向民众开枪。</p>\n<p>成千上万叙利亚人走上街头，参加在周五示威游行中被杀害者的葬礼。</p>\n<p>至少有72人在周五的抗议中被警方打死。</p>\n<p>国际社会对叙利亚当局的做法表示谴责。叙利亚官员则谴责黑帮是暴力的幕后黑手。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>\t<a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/world/2011/04/#page-top\" rel=\"nofollow\"><br />\n\t\t<span>点击</span><br />\n\t\t<span>页首</span><br />\n\t</a></div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/a4lhzhHXLSGbkvq7ToKblj4YjmA/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/a4lhzhHXLSGbkvq7ToKblj4YjmA/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/a4lhzhHXLSGbkvq7ToKblj4YjmA/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/a4lhzhHXLSGbkvq7ToKblj4YjmA/1/di\"></a></p>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/H9T6N1dANNg\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[19748]}